    "78": {
      "play": "FALSTAFF: What, a young knave and begging? Is there",
      "notes": []
    },
    "79": {
      "play": "not wars? Is there not employment? Doth not the",
      "notes": []
    },
    "80": {
      "play": "King lack subjects? Do not the rebels need soldiers?",
      "notes": []
    },
    "81": {
      "play": "Though it be a shame to be on any side but one, it is",
      "notes": []
    },
    "82": {
      "play": "worse shame to beg than to be on the worst side,",
      "notes": []
    },
    "83": {
      "play": "were it worse than the name of rebellion can tell",
