    "105": {
      "play": "FALSTAFF: He’s no swaggerer, hostess, a tame cheater, i’",
      "notes": [
        "He's no swaggerer, hostess...] Home (1762; 8 ed., 1805, ii. 269) cites this speech as an admirable depiction of character.",
        "cheater] ONIONS (1911): The modern sense."
