        "Pardon, sir, I have heard the word—\"phrase\" call you it? By this day] See textual notes. In both places many editors follow Qb instead of Qa and F. I do not know how it can reasonably be supposed that Qb has any authority whatever when it differs from Qa; see p. 476. Both"
      ]
