      "notes": []
    },
    "9": {
      "play": "ARCHBISHOP: ’Tis well done.",
      "notes": []
    },
    "10": {
      "play": "My friends and brethren in these great affairs,",
      "notes": []
    },
    "11": {
      "play": "I must acquaint you that I have received",
      "notes": [
        "New-dated] See note on I.ii.137."
      ]
    },
    "12": {
      "play": "New-dated letters from Northumberland,",
      "notes": []
