      "notes": [
        "] Deighton (ed. 1893): Who have lived to a good age in all the enjoyment of a peaceful life.",
        "good Letters] N.E.D. (Letter sb.^1 6): Good letters (obs.) [=erudition]. Occasionally, the profession of literature, authorship."
      ]
    },
    "53": {
      "play": "Whose white investments figure innocence,",
